dcterms:description: The Indian Pines dataset contains hyperspectral images with 16 vegetation classes and has a spatial resolution of 20 m by pixel. It includes 200 hyperspectral bands ranging from 400 nm to 2500 nm.

dcterms:description: The University of Pavia dataset includes hyperspectral images with 9 urban land cover types and has a spatial resolution of 1.3 m by pixel. It consists of 103 hyperspectral bands ranging from 430 nm to 860 nm.
